Install Bash Update Script

curl -s https://raw.github.com/nandub/sublime2-selfupdate/master/sl2update > sl2

chmod 755 sl2

sudo cp -p sl2 /usr/local/bin

Update Sublime Text 2

sl2 <build> [location] - location defaults to $PWD

sl2 2126 $HOME/devtools

and last add $HOME/devtools/sublime2 to your path and execute 'sublime_text' executable.